name: HomeKit Client
tagline: An app that was made by KhaosT.
body:
### Welcome!
HomeKit client allows you to add HomeKit devices, and customize them as you like. All of this is by @KhaosT, I just added a page and an IPA for it. 

### Authors and Contributors
@KhaosT for all of the code.
@128keaton forked, and shined it up and made it an IPA. 


### Support or Contact
Contact @128keaton at keaton@me.com.
